message.content:
Thoroughly explore the Claudish codebase at /Users/imorgado/Desktop/Development/Projects/claudish/ to understand:

1. **Model Router Architecture**: How does it switch between multiple AI providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Groq, etc.)?
2. **Configuration System**: How are models, API keys, and settings managed?
3. **CLI Interface**: What CLI framework is used? How are commands structured?
4. **Context Management**: Any token counting or context window handling?
5. **Error Handling**: How does it handle API failures and fallback to other models?
6. **Code Structure**: Main files, class hierarchy, reusable patterns

Find all TypeScript/JavaScript files related to model routing, CLI commands, and configuration. Extract the core architecture we can adapt for our new tool.

{
  "name": "claudish",
  "version": "3.2.0",
  "description": "Run Claude Code with any model - OpenRouter, Ollama, LM Studio & local models",
  "type": "module",
  "main": "./dist/index.js",
  "bin": {
    "claudish": "dist/index.js"
  },
  "scripts": {
    "dev": "bun run src/index.ts",
    "dev:mcp": "bun run src/index.ts --mcp",
    "dev:grok": "bun run src/index.ts --interactive --model x-ai/grok-code-fast-1",
    "dev:grok:debug": "bun run src/index.ts --interactive --debug --log-level info --model x-ai/grok-code-fast-1",
    "dev:info": "bun run src/index.ts --interactive --monitor",
    "extract-models": "bun run scripts/extract-models.ts",
    "build": "bun run extract-models && bun build src/index.ts --outdir dist --target node && chmod +x dist/index.js",
    "build:ci": "bun build src/index.ts --outdir dist --target node && chmod +x dist/index.js",
    "build:binary": "bun run extract-models && bun build src/index.ts --compile --outfile claudish",
    "build:binary:linux": "bun run extract-models && bun build src/index.ts --compile --target=bun-linux-x64 --outfile claudish-linux-x64",
    "build:binary:mac": "bun run extract-models && bun build src/index.ts --compile --target=bun-darwin-arm64 --outfile claudish-darwin-arm64",
    "link": "npm link",
    "unlink": "npm unlink -g claudish",
    "install-global": "bun run build && npm link",
    "kill-all": "pkill -f 'bun.*claudish' || pkill -f 'claude.*claudish-settings' || echo 'No claudish processes found'",
    "test": "bun test ./tests/comprehensive-model-test.ts",
    "typecheck": "tsc --noEmit",
    "lint": "biome check .",
    "format": "biome format --write .",
    "postinstall": "node scripts/postinstall.cjs"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@hono/node-server": "^1.19.6",
    "@inquirer/prompts": "^8.0.1",
    "@inquirer/search": "^4.0.1",
    "@modelcontextprotocol/sdk": "^1.22.0",
    "dotenv": "^17.2.3",
    "hono": "^4.10.6",
    "undici": "^7.16.0",
    "zod": "^4.1.13"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@biomejs/biome": "^1.9.4",
    "@types/bun": "latest",
    "@types/jest": "^30.0.0",
    "jest": "^30.2.0",
    "jest-environment-node": "^30.2.0",
    "typescript": "^5.9.3"
  },
  "files": ["dist/", "scripts/", "skills/", "AI_AGENT_GUIDE.md", "recommended-models.json"],
  "engines": {
    "node": ">=18.0.0",
    "bun": ">=1.0.0"
  },
  "preferGlobal": true,
  "keywords": [
    "claude",
    "claude-code",
    "openrouter",
    "proxy",
    "cli",
    "mcp",
    "model-context-protocol",
    "ai"
  ],
  "author": "Jack Rudenko <i@madappgang.com>",
  "license": "MIT",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/MadAppGang/claudish"
  }
}
